<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0212001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0212001">以下之諸偈出處不明。恐是四尼柯耶成立以後而製作者。MNd. 505; J. I, 117f; Vm. 388; DhpA. I. 246; Divyāvadāna P. 491；說一切有部毘奈耶卷三一（大正藏二二、七九七a）等參照。</note>
<note n="0213002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0213002">本偈由 S. I, 195 = Thag. 1249 之引用。CNd. 293；雜阿含一二一一經（大正藏二、三二九c以下），別譯雜阿含二二八經（大正藏二、四五七c）參照。</note>
<note n="0213003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0213003">山側（nagassa passe）S. 及 Thag. 雖為 nāgassa passe，如底本之 nagassa passe 為正。</note>
<note n="0213004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0213004">本偈由 Sn. 715 之引用。mahāvastu III, 388 參照。</note>
<note n="0213005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0213005">愛著（visaṭā）在底本雖有 paripatā，今從 PTS 本及引用原文。</note>
<note n="0214006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0214006">歸依所（saraṇa）底本之 carana 是誤植。</note>
<note n="0218007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0218007">心平等性（cittasamatā）在底本雖有 cittasamatho，今從 MNd. 501 之同文。</note>
<note n="0218008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0218008">心安息性（cittappassaddhatā）在底本雖有 cittappasādatā，今從 PTS 本及 MNd. 501 之同文。</note>
</p>
